1. Definitions
--------------

1.1. "Software" means the source code, object code, documentation, examples,
and other material in this repository that is identified as being provided
under this License.

1.2. "Licensor" means the copyright holder or copyright holders who make the
applicable Software available under this License.

1.3. "You" means an individual or legal entity exercising rights under this
License.

1.4. "Health-Sector Organization" means a legal entity whose business,
product, service, or principal operation involves healthcare delivery,
clinical or medical services, hospitals, clinics, laboratories, diagnostics,
pharmaceuticals, biotechnology, medical devices, health insurance, or the
management or processing of regulated health information. It also includes a
contractor, reseller, service provider, or other person acting on behalf of a
Health-Sector Organization for those activities.

1.5. "Health-Sector Use" means use of the Software by a Health-Sector
Organization in, or for, its health-sector business or operations, including
developing, testing, deploying, distributing, operating, supporting, or
providing a product or service for those activities. Health-Sector Use is
restricted whether it is commercial or non-commercial.

1.6. "Non-Health-Sector Use" means any use that is not Health-Sector Use.

