3. Health-Sector Licensing Requirement
---------------------------------------

A Health-Sector Organization may not exercise any right granted by Section 2
for Health-Sector Use under this License. Before making any Health-Sector Use,
the Health-Sector Organization must obtain a separate written commercial
license and any required permission from the Licensor.

A contractor, reseller, service provider, or other person acting for a
Health-Sector Organization may not avoid this requirement by obtaining or
using the Software in its own name. The separate written license must cover
the specific Health-Sector Use and must be signed by an authorized
representative of the Licensor.

Nothing in this License grants permission to use the Software for a
Health-Sector Use merely because the Software is publicly available, its
source code can be viewed, or a copy was obtained from a public repository.

